Life at OccidentalEarly CareerEmployee Development






Oxy Page Content Life at Occidental We treat every employee with respect and dignity while providing a positive, dynamic work environment with ample opportunities for professional growth.
   
   Full Time FAQs
 

​   What Employees SayEmployee Development We realize that Occidental’s success is a direct result of our employees’ achievements. We strive to hire individuals with the expertise, ingenuity, and vision necessary to succeed in our global enterprise.


   
         Global Opportunities


   
         Continuous LearningInternships  Occidental's internship program selects students with strong records of achievement to participate in a work program where they can develop the skills necessary to succeed in a competitive business environment.


   
         Campus Events


   
         Internship FAQs


   
         What Interns and Recent Grads Say


   
         Intern Projects


   
         Resume Tips Throughout this website, “Oxy” refers to one or more of Occidental Petroleum Corporation, a Delaware corporation, its subsidiaries, and affiliates. The potential careers or positions summarized on this website each relate to a specific employer, which may be Occidental Petroleum Corporation, a subsidiary, or an affiliate. 



























                                    
