Callout Image 1


Callout HTML 1Occidental 
   Petroleum Corporation offers rewarding careers in a fast-paced industry that shapes our world every day. At Occidental, we’re looking for creative, energetic people who are passionate about their field and want to learn, excel, and grow with one of the industry’s strongest performers. 
 

 

